6. - Goals

- Improve the graphics slightly, but maintain the "retro" look that
  characterized the original Pong.

- Improve randomization in how the ball starts and reacts to the
  paddles during the game.

- A menu for the beginning of the game.

- Get fullscreen working.

- Move to 800x600 resolution.
